OL,3,CP&O tells crew it will comply with
OL,4,CFrench law and reduce their hours
OL,6,FA letter, circulated on Friday,
OL,7,Finformed crew that by law they can no
OL,8,Flonger work for more than fourteen
OL,9,Fconsecutive days, followed by an
OL,10,Fequivalent rest period ashore.
OL,12,FThe letter says "the new regulation
OL,13,Fcomes into force in June 2024" and
OL,14,Fthat there would be "serious
OL,15,Fconsequences" for violation.
OL,17,FTwo years ago, P&O caused outrage on
OL,18,Fboth sides of the Channel by sacking
OL,19,F786 crew and replacing them with
OL,20,Fagency workers.
